-- MOVES-HSBC names Andy Maguire as Group Chief Operating Officer 
-- 
-- Wed Oct 22, 2014 05:32AM EDT
-- None



Oct 22 (Reuters) - HSBC Holdings Plc <HSBA.L> appointed Andy Maguire as group chief operating officer and group general manager, effective Dec. 1.

Andy is joining from Boston Consulting Group, where he is managing partner of the UK and Ireland, and a member of the firm's global executive committee.  Maguire will succeed Sean O'Sullivan, who is retiring after a 34-year career at HSBC.